$$
\begin{equation*}
V_{s d}=V_{b}-V_{a}=-\left(V_{a}-V_{b}\right) \quad \text { and } \quad V_{o d}=V_{y}-V_{x}=-\left(V_{x}-V_{y}\right) \tag{12.5}
\end{equation*}
$$

