since $V_{d s 31}=V_{d s 32}, V_{t 31}=V_{t 32}=V_{t n}$, and $(W / L)_{31}=(W / L)_{32}$. This equation indicates that $I_{c m s}$ depends on the CM output voltage and is independent of the differential output voltage
